## Feature Flags

Flags are defined in `feature_flags.yaml` and injected as environment variables at deploy time.

| Flag | Default | Description |
|------|---------|-------------|
{% for flag in flags -%}
| `{{ flag }}` | OFF | — |
{% else -%}
| — | — | No flags yet. Run `ymir feature start {{ name }} <flag>` |
{% endfor %}

To activate a flag locally:
```bash
export FEATURE_<FLAG>=true
```

## Deployment

```bash
# Start a feature
ymir feature start {{ name }} <flag>

# Test in dev (flag ON)
ymir feature activate-dev {{ name }} <flag>

# Dark launch to prod (flag OFF)
ymir deploy prod {{ name }} <flag>

# Release to users
ymir release {{ name }} <flag>

# Rollback
ymir deactivate-prod {{ name }} <flag>
```

